Clean, efficient, regularly updated Gentoo ebuilds for MythTV.

Full documentation:
https://github.com/ewestbrook/ew-mythtv-gentoo/wiki/

First time setup:
https://github.com/ewestbrook/ew-mythtv-gentoo/wiki/First-Time-Setup

1.  Clone this repo into a local directory
2.  Add that directory to PORTDIR_OVERLAY in /etc/make.conf
3.  (Optional) Mask and Unmask to taste
4.  (Optional) Edit USE flags to taste
5.  Emerge

Updating:
https://github.com/ewestbrook/ew-mythtv-gentoo/wiki/Updating

1.  Update your local repo
2.  Emerge

Full documentation at:
https://github.com/ewestbrook/ew-mythtv-gentoo/wiki/
